        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "@whitebyte The code change is trivial, and there is still a common use-case: slow SSH connection.\r\n\r\nMore generally I would like to add some default mapping that \"disables all fancy things\". This will allow us to more aggressively enable UI features (such as `'inccommand'`), but for slow environments one can hit the mapping. #6293",
