        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Neovim should actually behave like nottyfast w.r.t scrolling internally now, but if terminfo entries is missing nvim TUI might still emulate scrolling. (I have noticed vertically scrolling regions being disabled with `TERM=xterm` even if this is supported, not sure what the situation is with tmux/screen).",
